# .trivyignore
# CVEs suppressed from Trivy container scans.
#
# FORMAT (one per line, comment above each entry is REQUIRED):
#
#   # Reason: <why we're suppressing this>
#   # No patch available as of: <date>
#   # Review by: <date — set a calendar reminder>
#   # Ticket: <link>
#   CVE-XXXX-XXXXX
#
# ── IMPORTANT ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Never suppress a CVE without a comment.
# Suppressions with expired review dates fail the pipeline.
# Run quarterly review: grep "Review by" .trivyignore
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# (empty — add entries here as needed)
